title: EP.37: SCHOOL DISTRICT TRYING TO SHUT US DOWN, HEAT/CELTICS, WARRIORS/MAVERICKS, AND MUCH MORE!
description: Tune in and see why the school district is trying to shut down our 1V1. We also talk about who will win each NBA series and who will lead the league next season in the NFL in each stat category. Listen in for more!
dc:creator: Griffin Proctor & Joe Jokonya
